<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HOA Payment Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 100px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .header h2 {
      color: #777;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .header h3 {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #444;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .content h4 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .content p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #000;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
    }

    .stamp-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .stamp {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .stamp img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .signature-container {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 15px;
      color: #777;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h4>President of:  <%= prisident %></h4>
      <h4>Home Owners Association</h4>
      <h2>Property Info: <%= propertyAddress %></h2>
      <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
      <h3>To: <%= ownerName %></h3>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h4>Subject: Friendly Reminder: Payment of Overdue HOA Contribution</h4>
      <p>Dear <%= ownerName %>,</p>
      <p>This is a reminder regarding your HOA contribution for the month of <%= expiredMonth %>, which is currently overdue.</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Outstanding Amount:</span> $<%= outstandingAmount %></p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Due Date:</span> <%= dueDate %></p>
      <p>We kindly request that you complete this payment at your earliest convenience to avoid any late fees or disruptions in services.</p>
      <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter, and we appreciate your continued support for our community.</p>

      <div class="stamp-container">
        <div class="signature-container">
          <p>Warm regards,</p>
          <p>President of HOA</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stamp">
          <img src="<%= stampImageUrl %>" alt="Stamp">
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="contact-info"><%= contactInfo %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <a href="mailto:<%= contactInfo %>" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
